one example of many:

The Blue Alliance

Thunder Robotics - Team 876 (2016)

FIRST Robotics Competition team from Hatton-Northwood, North Dakota, USA.

To answer your question: a lot of the times gearing for surface speed of the wheels, however lobbing games bring wheel speed closer to intake speed.
